          <blockquote class="userstuff"><p>hey y'all! new chap! happy friday. we're here to introduce something we haven't had in this fic before (/j): character development! lmao. we hope you enjoy this chapter, and thanks for clicking! </p><p>as usual, if you're so inclined, you can find yourself some mood music <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4QOe9pYf1IL0BSrwEa6vPN?si=d92c29774a82459d" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p></blockquote>
