    </h3>

    <!-- only display byline if different from the main byline -->


      <div id="notes" class="notes module">
        <h3 class="heading">Notes:</h3>
          <blockquote class="userstuff"><p>hey there! welcome welcome to the opening of year 5 — the year that people get to be in charge of stuff!</p><p>this one is… [*<i>counts pages</i>*] longer than the last two years. not combined (i think /gen -fox), but definitely longer. hope yall enjoy our group of fourteen-turning-fifteen-year-olds!</p><p>as usual, if you're so inclined, you can find yourself some mood music <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4QOe9pYf1IL0BSrwEa6vPN?si=d92c29774a82459d" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p><p>thanks for clicking!</p></blockquote>
