</p><p>
  <span>She smiles, remembering that Alyssa had slipped the notebook under her nose in one of the few dull moments of class, showing her how her father had carefully calligraphed the prior page to read: </span>
  <em>
    <span>How to Survive Hogwarts (Mostly) Unscathed!</span>
  </em>
</p><p>
  <span>She can only assume that each page after accounts for the following years of schooling. </span>
