</p><p>
  <span>“If you want it, then you’ll have to get it!” He grins, pulling out his wand and casting a levitating charm on it, flying it through the courtyard. “That traitor Slytherin has been gone for years, hasn’t he? Why you reading this thing like you just got it?” </span>
