  <span>It causes an explosion of laughter from their entire friend group, and Emma finds her heart settle in her chest slightly. She looks to the sky for a moment, remembering suddenly the page Alyssa was reading. She closes her eyes, taking a breath before sending a silent message to Alyssa’s father, wherever he is. </span>
